krokit (1.0-a) stable; urgency=low

  * Implemented 'list' option to list deployed projects
  * Implemented 'refresh' option to refresh OpenGrok index
  * Added ignore patterns to the indexer
  * Updated OpenGrok logging properties
  * Changed short option of delete to '-D'
  * Updated Makefile to generate TARGET.out
  * Added Usage demo in README and help menu

 -- Kirubakaran Shanmugam <kribakarans@gmail.com>  Thu, 03 Nov 2022 14:25:25 +0530

